Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:02:01.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,THE SCREAMING OPERATION ROOM\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club concert starts at 3:00 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mountaineering Club Special...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mountain hut style fried noodles, try some!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Entry number five...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Third year English major...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arisugawa Arisa{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you not to break our set!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now what do we do with our show this evening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about some ice-chilled drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two more submarine-shaped UFOs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get movin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cosplay Photo Museum is now open!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, allow me to introduce!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An alumnus of Beika Umveristy as well as a prominent detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please welcome Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to visit your alma mater after such a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must feel nostalgic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The buildings are still run-down as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beautiful ladies sure are plentiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he was giving a speech at his alma\Nmater's festival, so I came to take a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But sure enough, he was after the female students!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why not let him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let him stretch his wings for once at an event like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing he's stretching is his horn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you stretch your wings in London, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You told me in an email that you\Nhappened to run into Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Signs}-kun{\r} there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you two did something you couldn't tell me, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of London!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you not butt in for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an adult conversation that has\Nnothing to do with a brat like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except it has everything to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since it's that Holmes geek we're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:04:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose he simply droned on about Holmes stuff and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SHIN'ICHI-KUN...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,CONFESSED TO YOU!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're too loud, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that son of a gun finally took the plunge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But under those circumstances, I wouldn't say he confessed to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a detective, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you call yourself a detective, then why\Ndon't you try to deduce what's in my heart!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really troublesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a troublesome, tough case, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With all these distracting emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I were Holmes, it'd still be impossible to figure out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The heart of the girl whom one likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can one accurately deduce that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But rather, it was you who forced him to confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you properly reply to him, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reply... about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Oh—Oh my god, I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I've always been in love with you too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I have to say anything like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wrong to have not said anything back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't spell it out for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Signs}-kun{\r} might think you rejected him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I definitely got the message back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to tell him, call him right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be your audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you going to do it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, I shall enumerate the 108 attributes\Na detective should never be without!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first being...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wisdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now there's no telling when he'll be done blabbering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not often that we get a great detective to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we had wanted to show him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mouri Kogoro's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you have some business with my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you have a case you want him to take on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you're his daughter, does that mean\Nyou've been to crime scenes with your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More than that, it's all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've seen some before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to go into this haunted house\Nand confirm the accuracy of the zombies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought that someone who's seen numerous\Nmurdered victims with their own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:03.04,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tsujiei Sonsaku (22)\NBeika University - 4th Year
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be able to give a more realistic assessment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, we're in the art track of the literature\Ndepartment, majoring in film studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're filming a horror movie for our final project.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But apparently the scene where one of\Nthe characters dies isn't realistic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.52,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hachiya Kiichi (22)\NBeika University - 4th Year
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or so says this annoying woman who thinks she's a genius director.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, when I asked her to use this\Nhaunted house and walk the walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with these folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When is Sleeping Kogoro coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we brought that detective's\Ndaughter and her friends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, they've said that they've seen murdered bodies before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, give your impressions to your dad after you see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And be sure to bring him here later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for our shift change!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what's this Mutsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't even got your make-up on yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're still going to fix my make-up even if I do it myself, right Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I thought it'd be better if I just\Nhad you do it for me from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:11.53,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Suguri Mutsumi (21)\NBeika University - 4th Year
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, guess I have no choice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll let these folks enter in thirty minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll want to show them your zombie act, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be prepared to feast your eyes upon the manner of my death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's going to be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all fake, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, even you were shocked just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was only because it was unexpected...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the whole point of haunted houses...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll never be able to tell Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Signs}-kun{\r}\Nthat you like him if you keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use this to strengthen your courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can clear this game, there's no doubt\Nyou'll step up to becoming a strong woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's super fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Super fun my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're that scared, how about we escort you through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We do know where each gimmick is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we gladly accept your offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because that way, even this girl will go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said it'll be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll only be scared at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just the beginning, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get lost, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been hugging me tight the entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's done pretty well for a\Nhaunted house at a campus festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bad taste, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wish Hashiguchi could have seen this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this haunted house and the horror movie final project...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were both planned by Hashiguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did that person drop out of school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just one month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard that his doctor told him he had an\Nincurable illness and only had half a year left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the suicide note found on him said he\Ntook his own life because of the torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, the ones who discovered his body were...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Us two and the ones you met earlier—\hMutsumi and Anna, the four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had nightmares from that for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That all of a sudden Anna became enthusiastic about the making\Nof the movie, saying it was in memory of the late Hashiguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Tsujiei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsujiei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where would he have gone off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was with us just a moment ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to check around here, so you guys go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The exit is straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it was straight ahead, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so dark, I can barely see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like theere's an operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure looks like they're doing an operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The patient is Anna{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r} from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doctors operating on her are mannequins, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The exit sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll have to pass beside the\Nhead of the bed in order to get out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be surprised at, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sort of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is just fake, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, don't be such crybabies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, something's wrong with Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the blood gushes out, she'd normally sit\Nup in bed and open her eyes with a snicker...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Anna, don't give us a raw deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to show us your grotesque manner of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, say something, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she not breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An almond scent from her mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take Anna to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an almond scent coming from her mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may have suffered from cyanide poisoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An almond scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't sniff, amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The almond scent is the smell of gas that results from the\Ningested poison reacting with the acid from her gastric fluids!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you breathe in too much of it, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's... what they said in the detective drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The so-called "almond scent" is not like the smell\Nof those sweet, fragrant nuts we usually eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they said it's the bittersweet smell of\Nthe almond plant before it's harvested!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with things as they seem now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anna{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r} most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Commited suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you're saying that she took the\Npoison herself right in front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 4th year in the art track of Beika University's\NLiterature Department, Tadami Anna{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the zombie make-up on, she looks completely different from\Nthe picture on the student ID that was in her belongings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the basis for saying that\NTadami Anna{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r} committed suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She suddenly appeared to be in great pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were just following this exit sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when we were passing by thelhead of the bed like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her body suddenly convulsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she struggled, thumping her feet repeatedly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So much that the entire bed shook and rattled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, blood shot out from her abdomen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wasn't the cause of death poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The coroner hasn't arrived yet so\we can't say so definitively, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An almond scent was coming from her mouth, and something\Nresembling a capsule was caught between her teeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was probably death by poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gushing blood was a gimmick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gimmick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the bed, there's a switch like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you press it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did it get on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does often fly over that way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's water-based so it should come right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the bed shaking was also a gimmick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a gimmick, but it's just that the upper right bedpost...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the lower left bedpost diagonal from it are slightly shortened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the actor lying, on the bed playing the patient rocks their body...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bed also shakes and rattles in response to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, her feet repeatedly\Nstriking the bed was also a trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can only be done...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the person lying in the bed themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, see for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from the mechanism for the\Nblood spray, there isn't anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do not touch the crime scene without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those feet with the red pedicure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw it from here when she was thumping her feet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sheet on top had come off, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her right foot came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It certainly seems as though she took the poison while\NRan{\rHonorifics - Signs}-kun{\r}'s group was passing by the head of the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, there wasn't anyone else in her vicinity, was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially near her face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was dark, but I think it was just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone had forced her to take the\Npoison, I think we should've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where were you all when she showed signs of pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was about to sneak up on those girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Putting this on my chest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were with those folks the whole time in the\Nrole of their guides through this haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I pretended to have gotten lost\Nmidway and put on a simple trick item...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To startle them in the operation room\Njust like Hachiya and I arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, after we parted ways, Tsujiei and I each did our own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in the X ray room next door...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'd been waiting for the guests to come the entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no one came even after I heard\Ntheir screams, so I got anxious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:19:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From this operation room, you have to go through\Nthat X-ray room in order to get to the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I came to check and see what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Anna was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anna was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mutsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your tears are messing up your make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anna just died, you know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys sure are taking it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could we be taking it well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We feel the same way as when Hashiguchi committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know about it since you're a detective right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case where a 4th year Beika University student\Ncommi e suici e y poison in isapa men a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if I recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His body was found by some colleagues who\Nhad happened to come to visit his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And those "colleagues" were myself, Tsujiei, Mutsumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Anna here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Hashiguchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was putting so much work into the final movie project, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't show up at the university for a whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got worried, so we decided to go together\Nand check up on him after classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we rang the doorbell, there was no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thinking that he was probably asleep or had gone\Nout, we decided to come back at a later time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then Anna said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's ask the manager to unlock the door
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After her suggestion, we went in and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how you found Hashiguchi{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r} who\Nhad committed suicide via poison, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In his room, there was a suicide note in his own handwriting:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Recently I started not feeling well, so I went to the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"But I was told I had an advanced malignant\Ntumor with only six months to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll leave the rest to you all, and I shall go\Non a head to see the world beyond death."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We asked the police after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And learned that he had died on that\Nday when we were all in a lecture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was after that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Anna started to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying that it was for Hashiguchi, she suddenly started to work\Non the final movie project and this haunted house feverishly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't it normal to put in extra effort for a friend who has passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it just wasn't normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even took too many sleeping pills once\Nand had to be taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her reason was that she wanted to experience a life-or-death\Nsituation in order to study the realistic manner of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one time when we wondered why she was silent\Nshe had actually kept a nail in her mouth the entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nail!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put the capsule containing poison into her mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the nail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if she accidently bit it by chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're saying she attempted to experience a\Nnear-death situation, but she actually died from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we surmised, this appears to be a case of suicide, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's really the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Signs}-kun{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this lady's cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The marks aren't make-up but look like they were really scratched...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's even blood oozing from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't this mean that someone was forcing her mouth shut...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she was trying to pry the arm away\Nleaving her fingernail marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's skin and blood underneath her fingernails!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a murder case disguised as a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit who poisoned Anna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mutsumi{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r}, you're the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Haichiya Knchi{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r}, you're the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.23,0:24:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been fidgeting this whole time, Tsujiei{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your guilt is causing you to act suspiciously, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.07,0:24:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are red lines on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anna{\rHonorifics - Signs}-san{\r} had already been poisoned to death.
